---
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../../consts';
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = SITE_TITLE + ' | About Me';
const description = `I am Milad as an experienced Software Engineer with over 9
        years in web services, I've been working on countless projects, each
        presenting its unique potentials and challenges. Every challenge
        overcome has enriched my knowledge base and fine-tuned my expertise. My
        journey thus far has fueled my desire to share my accumulated wealth of
        knowledge, and that's why this Sign Language Tech was born into here.`;
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <main>
    <h2>Bridging the gap: web development in sign language</h2>

    <div class='profile'>
      <img class='profile-photo' src='/slt-my-profile-light.webp' alt="Milad profile"/>
      <p class='mb-2'>
        Hey there! I am Milad as an experienced Software Engineer with over 9
        years in web services, I've been working on countless projects, each
        presenting its unique potentials and challenges. Every challenge
        overcome has enriched my knowledge base and fine-tuned my expertise. My
        journey thus far has fueled my desire to share my accumulated wealth of
        knowledge, and that's why this Sign Language Tech was born into here.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h3>Why Sign Language Tech?</h3>

    <p class='mb-2'>
      Well, Here, you'll find extensive, professional, and comprehensive
      discussions on web development, delivered in a captivating and
      user-friendly manner with International/American Sign Language. Beyond
      coding and software language, I want to bridge the communication gap and
      make this intriguing world of web development accessible to the deaf
      community. An important part of my mission is to bring on-board deaf
      experts who will share their valuable insights accumulated from years of
      experience in their respective fields. My hope is that their unique
      perspectives and advice will present you with a more profound
      understanding of the multiple approaches and objectives prevalent in our
      field.
    </p>

    <h3>Interactive Learning Opportunities</h3>

    <p class='mb-2'>
      However, this is not only about tutorials and interviews. I also plan to
      organize interactive events where experts can offer presentations and
      productive workshops. This will not only provide an opportunity for you to
      interact with experts but also offer the chance to learn from more
      hands-on experiences. This platform is dedicated to supporting your career
      growth, fostering community spirit, and providing relevant workshops to
      hone your skills. Stay tuned and join us on this enlightening journey in
      web development!
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .profile {
    display: flex;
  }

  .profile p {
    padding-left: 40px;
  }

  .profile-photo {
    height: 200px;
    width: 200px;
    padding: 1em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .profile {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .profile p {
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    .profile-photo {
      height: 100px;
      width: 100px;
    }
  }
</style>
